---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="EU AI Act Implementation Timeline | AiLex Consulting"
  description="Professional guide to EU AI Act enforcement dates, compliance requirements, and penalty framework. Expert analysis of critical implementation milestones."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Professional Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-50 to-blue-50 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-6">
            EU AI Act Implementation <span class="text-blue-800">Timeline</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Systematic implementation schedule establishing regulatory obligations from August 2024 through August 2026. GPAI model requirements commence August 2, 2025, with full enforcement penalties reaching €35 million. <em class="text-blue-800">SCIENTIA ET LEX</em> — professional compliance through regulatory precision.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">Aug '24</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Entry Force</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">Feb '25</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Prohibitions</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">Aug '25</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">GPAI Models</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-700">Aug '26</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Full Compliance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Critical Implementation Timeline -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">When Do EU AI Act Requirements Come Into Effect?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Systematic implementation schedule with enforcement milestones</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- August 2024 - Entry into Force -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-green-700 font-semibold text-sm">✓</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mr-3">August 1, 2024 — Entry into Force</h3>
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">COMPLETED</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">EU AI Act officially entered force, establishing legal framework and beginning implementation timeline.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- February 2025 - Prohibitions -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-amber-700 font-semibold text-sm">!</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mr-3">February 2, 2025 — Prohibitions Active</h3>
                <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">ACTIVE</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Banned AI practices prohibited. AI literacy obligations commence requiring staff competency in AI systems operation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- August 2025 - GPAI Models -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-red-700 font-semibold text-sm">⚡</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mr-3">August 2, 2025 — GPAI Obligations</h3>
                <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">CRITICAL</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">General-purpose AI model governance, transparency obligations, and systemic risk management requirements active.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- August 2026 - Full Implementation -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-6 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-purple-700 font-semibold text-sm">⭐</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mr-3">August 2, 2026 — Full Compliance</h3>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">FINAL</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Complete compliance required for all high-risk AI systems including risk management, transparency, and human oversight.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Penalty Framework -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">What Are the EU AI Act Penalty Levels?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Three-tier penalty framework based on violation severity</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Prohibited Practices -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border-2 border-red-200">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                <span class="text-red-700 text-2xl">⛔</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Prohibited Practices</h3>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700 mt-2">€35M</div>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm">or 7% global turnover</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Subliminal manipulation techniques</li>
              <li>• Exploiting vulnerable populations</li>
              <li>• Social scoring systems</li>
              <li>• Real-time biometric identification</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- High-Risk Systems -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border-2 border-amber-200">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                <span class="text-amber-700 text-2xl">⚠️</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">High-Risk Violations</h3>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-700 mt-2">€15M</div>
              <p class="text-amber-600 text-sm">or 3% global turnover</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Non-compliant risk management</li>
              <li>• Inadequate data governance</li>
              <li>• Missing human oversight</li>
              <li>• Insufficient documentation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Other Violations -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border-2 border-blue-200">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                <span class="text-blue-700 text-2xl">ℹ️</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Other Violations</h3>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mt-2">€7.5M</div>
              <p class="text-blue-600 text-sm">or 1.5% global turnover</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Incorrect authority information</li>
              <li>• Non-cooperation with regulators</li>
              <li>• GPAI model non-compliance</li>
              <li>• AI literacy violations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ for AEO -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">How Should Organisations Prepare for EU AI Act Deadlines?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">What is the most critical EU AI Act deadline?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">August 2, 2025 represents the critical GPAI model compliance deadline, requiring governance rules, transparency obligations, and systemic risk management for general-purpose AI systems.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">How long do organisations have to achieve full compliance?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Full EU AI Act compliance must be achieved by August 2, 2026, providing organisations 24 months from current date to implement comprehensive high-risk system requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Professional Consultation -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-slate-900 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-6">Professional Implementation Guidance</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Systematic compliance preparation ensuring readiness for critical implementation milestones.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4 md:flex md:justify-center">
          <a href="/emergency-assessment" class="inline-block bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Emergency Assessment — £9,500
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Schedule Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mt-6 text-sm">Professional preparation • Regulatory certainty • Implementation roadmap</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Schema Markup -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the most critical EU AI Act deadline?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "August 2, 2025 represents the critical GPAI model compliance deadline, requiring governance rules, transparency obligations, and systemic risk management for general-purpose AI systems."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How long do organisations have to achieve full compliance?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Full EU AI Act compliance must be achieved by August 2, 2026, providing organisations 24 months from current date to implement comprehensive high-risk system requirements."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .font-serif { font-family: Georgia, serif; }
</style>